# Memory-Bank Protocol — Project Filum

> 同步自 `AGENT_RULES.md`；三态结构 runtime/logs/knowledge

## 🔥 HOT
`knowledge/project-brief` · `knowledge/architecture` · `knowledge/contracts/data-contracts` · `knowledge/contracts/repository-contract` · `knowledge/conventions` · `runtime/active-task`

## 🌡️ WARM
`knowledge/roadmap` · `logs/changelog` · `knowledge/domains/*` · `knowledge/plans/*` · `knowledge/manuals/*` · `design-document` · `tech-stack` · 子项目 README · `DESIGN.md`(前端任务时)

## 🧊 COLD
`knowledge/decisions/*` · `knowledge/known-issues/*` · `knowledge/glossary` · `history/` · `archive/`

## Update
会话结束追加 `logs/progress/progress.md`；schema→`knowledge/contracts/data-contracts`；架构→`knowledge/architecture`；ADR→`knowledge/decisions/` 独立文件；坑位→`knowledge/known-issues/` 独立文件；版本→`VERSION`+`logs/changelog`；运行 `python .paradigma/tools/pd-check-all.py`
